<dl class="quick-answers" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr).);gap:16px;">
  <div><dt style="font-weight:700;color:var(--blue);">Trade licence transferable on premises sale?</dt><dd>No - it is location and applicant-specific. The new occupant must apply fresh.</dd></div>
